The `polysim_clob_client` package provides a drop-in-compatible surface
modeled on the public API of py-clob-client
(https://github.com/Polymarket/py-clob-client), which is distributed
under the MIT License. No source code from py-clob-client is included or
redistributed here; only its public method/return shapes are mirrored so
existing integrations can switch with minimal changes. "Polymarket" and
"py-clob-client" are referenced for interoperability and identification
purposes only; this project is not affiliated with or endorsed by
Polymarket.
